---
// src/components/Pricing.astro
---
<section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-24">
  <div class="text-center mb-16">
    <div class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 text-sm font-bold text-indigo-700 bg-indigo-100 mb-6 ring-1 ring-inset ring-indigo-500/20">Investissement</div>
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tight">Des tarifs clairs, orientés rentabilité</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Pas de coûts cachés, pas de mauvaises surprises. Choisissez le partenariat qui correspond à vos ambitions de croissance en Suisse.</p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 items-center max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Pack 1 : Vitrine -->
    <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Site Vitrine Standard</h3>
      <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mb-6">La fondation parfaite pour asseoir votre crédibilité locale.</p>
      <div class="mb-6 flex items-baseline gap-2">
        <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-500">Dès</span>
        <span class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900">1'500</span>
        <span class="text-slate-500 font-medium">CHF</span>
      </div>
      <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8 text-sm text-slate-600">
        <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-600 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
          Design vitrine ultra-rapide
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-600 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
          Conformité stricte nLPD
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-600 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
          Hébergement sécurisé suisse
        </li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/contact" class="block text-center w-full rounded-xl bg-slate-100 text-slate-900 font-bold py-3 hover:bg-slate-200 transition-colors">Demander un devis</a>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Pack 2 : Performance & ROI (Mise en avant) -->
    <div class="bg-indigo-600 p-8 rounded-3xl border border-indigo-600 shadow-xl shadow-indigo-600/20 transform md:-translate-y-4 relative group hover:shadow-indigo-600/40 transition-all duration-300">
      <div class="absolute top-0 right-6 transform -translate-y-1/2">
        <span class="bg-indigo-300 text-indigo-900 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider py-1 px-3 rounded-full shadow-sm">Recommandé</span>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Performance & ROI</h3>
      <p class="text-indigo-200 text-sm mb-6">Le système complet pour générer un flux de clients continu.</p>
      <div class="mb-6 flex items-baseline gap-2 text-white">
        <span class="text-sm font-bold text-indigo-200">Dès</span>
        <span class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold">3'500</span>
        <span class="text-indigo-200 font-medium">CHF</span>
      </div>
      <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8 text-sm text-indigo-100">
        <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
          Design sur-mesure & Copywriting
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
          Optimisation SEO locale poussée
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
          Automatisation IA de l'acquisition
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
          Maintenance & Support prioritaire
        </li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/contact" class="block text-center w-full rounded-xl bg-white text-indigo-600 font-bold py-4 hover:bg-indigo-50 transition-colors shadow-sm transform group-hover:scale-[1.02]">Lancer ma croissance</a>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Pack 3 : Sur-mesure -->
    <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Sur-mesure & E-com</h3>
      <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mb-6">Pour les projets complexes ou les boutiques en ligne.</p>
      <div class="mb-6">
        <span class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900">Sur devis</span>
      </div>
      <ul class="space-y-4 mb-8 text-sm text-slate-600 mt-2">
        <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-600 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
          Boutique E-commerce complète
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-600 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
          Développement d'applications Web
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-600 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
          Architectures API / Intégration CRM
        </li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/contact" class="block text-center w-full rounded-xl bg-slate-100 text-slate-900 font-bold py-3 hover:bg-slate-200 transition-colors">Contacter les experts</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
